text:
New White House press sec ends her first briefing by saying Trump is off to Camp David for the weekend & reminding people to tune into his Fox News town hall. 

"It'll be can't miss television, much like the highly-rated President Trump coronavirus task force briefings have been" https://t.co/KBnu46KqFB
